column5: Hey guys  my name is Imran and i was wondering if anyone would like to come steel heading  for trout opener  tomorrow I'm a mature 15 year old  who has been fishing for 7 years . we would be fishing the credit in brampton on my parents private  let me know thanks
This sounds like a plenty of fish ad.  You might get some bites, lol.
Nice offer,would love to ,but this weekend is out for me.Are you able to go during the week?,or just weekends only?
Nice offer,would love to ,but this weekend is out for me.Are you able to go during the week?,or just weekends only? week days are ok
Little far for me Imran but wish ya good luck lad.  A friendly offer to anyone looking for a day out with company.
